  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/510becca36848c11efb9937d1006fe60.webp?t=1743668024\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“COROCONNECT\" is a multiplayer-only action game. The key to this game is the teamwork! Players use wonder gimmicks to tackle different stages. Synchronized cooperation is essential for success! Team up with friends or online players to clear all the stages!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/2a489d4924b261acfd43e95a3ebc751e.poster.avif?t=1743668024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/2a489d4924b261acfd43e95a3ebc751e.webm?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/2a489d4924b261acfd43e95a3ebc751e.mp4?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/4bfecfe6ad8db250e968a719bed0293b.webp?t=1743668024\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"COROCONNECT\" is currently in Early Access. We would love to hear your thoughts and feedback! Bug reports, improvement suggestions, and ideas are all welcome. Together, we aim to create an even better game with your help.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/5ef08bfd4c60d84bf9f654e86dd61f4d.poster.avif?t=1743668024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/5ef08bfd4c60d84bf9f654e86dd61f4d.webm?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/5ef08bfd4c60d84bf9f654e86dd61f4d.mp4?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/adb9ff2e7ead3b2dd2a89735d7b684f7.webp?t=1743668024\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer-only game</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 4 players online or locally</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each player's actions are crucial. The unique gameplay requires cooperation with teammates to clear stages.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of gimmicks: Players can freely switch between 4 types of gimmicks, and using the same gimmick can sometimes provide an advantage.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging stages: Each stage is meticulously designed to test players' skills and teamwork.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/6d1c0817e5c514528d3e56935989d52f.poster.avif?t=1743668024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/6d1c0817e5c514528d3e56935989d52f.webm?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/6d1c0817e5c514528d3e56935989d52f.mp4?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While COROCONNECT supports Remote Play, please note that only Player 1 (the host player) can use a keyboard and mouse. Players 2-4 must use controllers to participate in the game.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/510becca36848c11efb9937d1006fe60.webp?t=1743668024\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“COROCONNECT\" is a multiplayer-only action game. The key to this game is the teamwork! Players use wonder gimmicks to tackle different stages. Synchronized cooperation is essential for success! Team up with friends or online players to clear all the stages!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/2a489d4924b261acfd43e95a3ebc751e.poster.avif?t=1743668024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/2a489d4924b261acfd43e95a3ebc751e.webm?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/2a489d4924b261acfd43e95a3ebc751e.mp4?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/4bfecfe6ad8db250e968a719bed0293b.webp?t=1743668024\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"COROCONNECT\" is currently in Early Access. We would love to hear your thoughts and feedback! Bug reports, improvement suggestions, and ideas are all welcome. Together, we aim to create an even better game with your help.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/5ef08bfd4c60d84bf9f654e86dd61f4d.poster.avif?t=1743668024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/5ef08bfd4c60d84bf9f654e86dd61f4d.webm?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/5ef08bfd4c60d84bf9f654e86dd61f4d.mp4?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/adb9ff2e7ead3b2dd2a89735d7b684f7.webp?t=1743668024\" width=615 height=40 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiplayer-only game</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play with up to 4 players online or locally</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each player's actions are crucial. The unique gameplay requires cooperation with teammates to clear stages.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of gimmicks: Players can freely switch between 4 types of gimmicks, and using the same gimmick can sometimes provide an advantage.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging stages: Each stage is meticulously designed to test players' skills and teamwork.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/6d1c0817e5c514528d3e56935989d52f.poster.avif?t=1743668024\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/6d1c0817e5c514528d3e56935989d52f.webm?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1729640/extras/6d1c0817e5c514528d3e56935989d52f.mp4?t=1743668024\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While COROCONNECT supports Remote Play, please note that only Player 1 (the host player) can use a keyboard and mouse. Players 2-4 must use controllers to participate in the game.</p>",
